parameters:
Would you like to view the event? The Upper-Class Pet
Introduction Event.

\nc<Senpai>...Well then, I'm counting on you for this week too. Oh, and
Saki, there's a special task for you.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>A special task? Does that mean it's going to be especially
tough?
\nc<Saki>Sigh... Where do I need to go...?

\nc<Senpai>Remember the VIP who brought a pet last time? That person
wants to invite Saki to an exclusive pet club event.
\nc<Employee 1>What's with the pale face? Pets are cute, aren't they?

\nc<Employee 2>Well... The pet that was brought last time was apparently a
large breeding slime...
\nc<Saki>Why does it have to be me again?!?

\nc<Senpai>Who knows. Maybe Saki has become popular among the pets as
being tasty?

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Are the slimes going to have a social gathering or
something?
\nc<Senpai>Curious? Then go check it out for yourself.

\nc<Saki>Ugh, being nominated by a VIP means I basically have no
right to refuse, right?

\nc<Senpai>You know it. I like it when Saki gives up quickly. Here's
the address.
\nc<Saki>If I don't come back, please come rescue me quickly...
